726309f-b.title: Queens: Caldwell Avenue - 61st Road
726309f-b.text:
Caldwell Avenue north side, east of 6lst Road (formerly Fleming
Jlace) showing in a semicircle from fore to extreme left background,
the homes of Charles Schmeig and one Kogelsberger in 1909. The houses
in the three views located in the background face on Dry Harbor Road.
In view one in the center background is seen the house of Michael
Brand in 1873. At the extreme left is the home of J. Trepne of that
time.
April 1923
Views 1,2 and 3
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
